                                <div style="background:#fef2f2; padding:1rem; border-radius:var(--radius-sm); border:1px solid #fca5a5;">
                                    <div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">
                                        <span style="font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:700; color:#b91c1c;">국방비 (GDP 대비)</span>
                                        <span style="font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:800; color:#dc2626;">4.12% (NATO 1위)</span>
                                    </div>
